{"tid":1321216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拋磚」針對新城市廣場引狗入室事件，以後可以點保護同行者後路？","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:59:38.000Z","uid":128151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45c08991c1e980687997e101448925fdf6bcd462","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"尋日新城市廣場發生左咁多事，我相信大家都好痛心。<br />\n<code>發夢見到大家打狗真係覺得好治癒#yup#</code><br />\n睇返過去咁多次行動都知，係有狗災既時候，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">商場</span></span>可以話係行人既頭等避難點。<br />\n但經過左尋日沙田既事，連最後既安全地點都受到威脅，我覺得大家好應該分析同考慮點樣應對今次/以後既可能情況。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下拋磚</span><br />\n睇返<span style=\"color: gold;\">新地聲明</span>，佢地話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇報警</span>，同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公共通道理應24小時開放</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190715/s00001/1563186721191/【逃犯條例-沙田示威】新地聲明-事前不知警進商場行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00001%2F1563186721191%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%B0%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E4%BA%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=a4ac4828\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00001%2F1563186721191%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%B0%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E4%BA%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&h=1a2c3945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190715/s00001/1563186721191/【逃犯條例-沙田示威】新地聲明-事前不知警進商場行動</a><br />\n<br />\n但岩岩<span style=\"color: gold;\">HK01</span>又出新聞指出好多早期起既商場地契都有條例會列出：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警務處處長及其人員可暢通無阻地進出</span>（uninterupted access），<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">並可在地契的範圍內執法</span>（in the pursuance of their lawful duties）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/352235/沙田遊行-新城市廣場地契准警隨時進入執法-示威者無路可退\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F352235%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%80&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=5e4ba7fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/352235/沙田遊行-新城市廣場地契准警隨時進入執法-示威者無路可退</a><br />\n<br />\n咁問題黎了，係咪以後所有商場對出黎野餐行街血拼（i.e. Shopping）既市民唔再安全？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面提到過既地契條例，重點在於「lawful duties」，<span style=\"color: red;\">即係除左執法以外，警方係冇權係私人商場自出自入既。</span><br />\n<br />\n我地先睇<span style=\"color: gold;\">警察通例</span>第44章04段落，講明<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警務人員如未獲得合法授權或擁有人╱佔用人的同意，不得進入任何處所搜查。</span></span> 而佢係英文版到，處所係譯做premises，而commercial premises （e.g. 商場）係其中一種。<br />\n<br />\n英文原版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/en/Epgo044.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Fen%2FEpgo044.pdf&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=6e12a3d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/en/Epgo044.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n但係，如果我地睇埋<span style=\"color: gold;\">警隊條例</span>Cap232 Section 50 - 3，就會發現<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警方只要懷疑有「應被拘捕」既人  （i.e. any person to be arrested）係個場所內，佢就可以係冇搜查令/物業持有人既同意下入去執法。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nCap. 232 Police Force Ordinance ─ Section 50 Arrest, detention and bail of suspected persons and seizure of suspected property<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!en?INDEX_CS=N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap232%21en%3FINDEX_CS%3DN&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=3438c430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!en?INDEX_CS=N</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢到就出現左個爭議點，咩叫「any person to be arrested」</span>？如果係指實質存在有名有姓既嫌疑人，引用返譚文豪議員講既一段說話 <br />\n<br />\n立法會議員譚文豪稱，雖然地契條款內列明警方可入內執法，但當日新城市廣場內沒有任何違法行為，而<span style=\"color: red;\">警員初時亦非入內進行拘捕工作</span>，認為警方「<span style=\"color: red;\">無法可執</span>」。他續稱，大部分示威者進入商場，其實只為了和平散去，批評警方當時的行動不合理，質疑警方刻意為暴力清場製造假象，並不斷演繹自己的權力。<br />\n<br />\n咁好明顯警方就係濫權加違例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，樓主利申定自己冇讀過law先，打咁多都係希望有讀開law既巴絲可以幫手解釋下 。幫未來既各位同路人鋪定後路，唔好比佢地誤入陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下開放討論</span></span><br />\n<br />\nreference<br />\nCap. 502 Fire Safety (Commercial Premises) Ordinance<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap502&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=e819ba2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap502</a>"},{"pid":"c38a1bb6e153cd6f4a2f5095b090bd546ff358c4","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"264cc722a6c89719d4a0e9c05e29d5c8162e0ac0","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"975a41147ecef311af41b0a0608349bf879fb5a4","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"0e9970a8bb0a73394b43423a0937e7cfc9dd2c9b","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"cb8ed3c18ea32e3588184bf0608b5aaafd71ada8","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"7d79ddf51b79741a14e258bd5e13db85b6b2f255","tid":1321216,"uid":133903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"誠邀law jj瘋狂討論"},{"pid":"9510afbcc36549e482f679d9c90905bf0b09abdf","tid":1321216,"uid":134502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"見樓主拋磚 分享少少基本法29 條入面對home and other premises 既意思<br />\n<br />\n第29 條講到the Homes and other premises of Hong Kong resident shall be inviolable . Arbitrary or unlawful search of, or intrusion into, a resident&rsquo;s home or other premises shall be prohibited. 簡單咁講姐係香港市民既私人地方唔可以侵犯， 唔可以不合法咁搜.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdzNy62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdzNy62.png&h=cc09be8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但留意返第24 條既定義Hong Kong resident 只係包natural person （既係自然人） 唔包legal person(法人）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZdZqeR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZdZqeR.png&h=8f17339a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果加埋樓主 、HK01 既睇法， 有冇人搵到邊條法例係講警方要係法人或其代表邀請既情況先可以入去私人地方？"},{"pid":"9d7c1c3455c30a98ca1d5fb1caeaa053c2937f7c","tid":1321216,"uid":134502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"Push 要讀law 既幫手"},{"pid":"216176ad1f56b13623cfc5b480b857976fbc811d","tid":1321216,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"a41ba99e3ea1e28a148bcb1e6abebbbb27843144","tid":1321216,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:49:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e20bd57966